      {{findings with ID (F1.N), severity, file:line, description}}

      ### 2. Error Handling Consistency
      {{findings with ID (F2.N)}}

      ### 3. Logging Consistency
      {{findings with ID (F3.N)}}

      ### 4. Type Safety
      {{findings with ID (F4.N)}}

      ### 5. Dead Code
      {{findings with ID (F5.N)}}

      ### 6. Test Consistency
      {{findings with ID (F6.N)}}

      ### 7. Comment Quality
      {{findings with ID (F7.N)}}

      ### 8. Config/Schema Alignment
      {{findings with ID (F8.N)}}

      ### 9. Dependency Hygiene
      {{findings with ID (F9.N)}}

      ### 10. Cross-File Pattern Drift
      {{findings with ID (F10.N)}}

