      ## Recommendations Summary

      {{prioritized recommendations table — CRITICAL, HIGH, MEDIUM only}}

      ---

      ## Overall Assessment

      {{detailed assessment — 2-3 paragraphs expanding on executive summary}}

      ---

      ## Codebase Metrics

      ### Test Coverage
      {{per-file coverage table}}

      ### Size and Testing Investment
      {{metrics table}}

      ### Complexity Metrics
